纯功能。其中，使用现代芋头为发酵原料蒸馏的出酒时间为 20 分钟，平均为 22 度；使用 50 度回糟酒蒸馏的出酒时间为 36 分钟，可提纯至 70 度。专家认为，此次实验证明在西汉就已存在相对高超的蒸馏技术。 海昏侯考古推断刘贺有条件喝上 20 多度的芋头酒"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-3aad46531e51edee08944b7b98c6e25e_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "热度累计中", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/7134954210"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIlsm948Dy7PoCEAMaCTExMjQwMzc1OCDyn4a7BjAAOCNAG3IKNzEzNDk1NDIxMHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1735103436.618672", "card_id": "Q_6684039531", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 54}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "待业一年，不敢面对任何社交、完全自我封闭，我到底在「怕」什么？持续封闭下去会有心理危害吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-fe6b8adf45601ccead3e5c8627d76d76_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "热度累计中", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/6684039531"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIlsm948Dy7PoCEAMaCTExMjMxMzQ5NyCVg+u6BjAAOM8CQBxyCjY2ODQwMzk1MzF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1735103436.618879", "card_id": "Q_391249733", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 158}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如果评选出武侠小说中的四大名著，你觉得哪四本可以入选？为什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-b22ad2354ab839db469cf8e2ec330838_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "热度累计中", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/391249733"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ilsm948Dy7PoCEAMaCDQ5MjIyNTE4IIaKoPUFMAA42QJAHXIJMzkxMjQ5NzMzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTS